{"title":"架自己的Blog | Setup Mine Blog Website","uid":"bfdfc9c5882f06218e9538cd9c76a553","slug":"Website Setup Experience","date":"2026-02-15T04:30:00.000Z","updated":"2026-06-12T17:35:50.576Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Website Setup Experience.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"架設網站心得\"><a href=\"#架設網站心得\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"架設網站心得\"></a>架設網站心得</h1><p>我過去一直以為Blog是甚麼老人才會用的撥接式網路那個年代的產物，結果我後來發現這東西其實蠻流行的。<br>之前也有嘗試問AI去做但每次都不知道為甚麼都會報錯，身邊也都沒有很熟的人有做過Blog，後來就不了了之。<br>一直到參加 <a href=\"/post/SCISTxSCAICT%202026.html\" title=\"SCISTxSCAICT 2026 聯合寒訓\">SCISTxSCAICT 2026 聯合寒訓</a> 之後認識了WalNut，我們兩個住同一間房間，後來我看到他也有做Blog，然後我就問他能不能也幫我搞一個，想不到跟他盧一下下他就答應了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/image/WebsiteSetupExperience1.png\" alt=\"alt text\"></p>\n<p>他幫我把前面搞資料夾的工作搞好了，我只需要把一些數據改一改然後推到Github上就行了<br>大概過了兩三天，我的Blog終於上線了！也就是你現在看到的這個網站！<br>這幾天感謝很多人幫忙，中途還出了一點小插曲…</p>\n<h2 id=\"小插曲\"><a href=\"#小插曲\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"小插曲\"></a>小插曲</h2><p>正常流程是先跑 <code>hexo clean</code> <code>hexo g</code> <code>hexo s</code> 甚麼的，結果在跑測試的時候不小心搞到整個爆掉。<br>本來想說去把Github上正常版本的抓回來回朔，然後我不小心跑成 <code>hexo d</code> !!!!!!<br>後來要去找以前的版本，然後不小心在後台<strong>把它刪了</strong>……<br>我真的是差一點爆炸，最後你猜怎麼救回來的?<br><br><br><br><code>CTRL+Z</code><br><br><br><br>好啦至少救回來了。<br>大概就是這樣啦~</p>\n<h1 id=\"Website-Setup-Experience\"><a href=\"#Website-Setup-Experience\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Website Setup Experience\"></a>Website Setup Experience</h1><p>I used to think blogs were some ancient relic from the dial-up era that only old people used, but I later realized they’re actually still pretty popular.<br>I tried asking AI to help me build one before, but for some reason, it kept throwing errors. Since I didn’t know anyone personally who had experience with blogging, I eventually just gave up.<br>That was until I attended <a href=\"/post/SCISTxSCAICT%202026.html\" title=\"SCISTxSCAICT 2026 聯合寒訓\">SCISTxSCAICT 2026 United Winter Camp</a> and met WalNut. We were roommates, and when I saw he had his own blog, I asked if he could help me set one up. Surprisingly, after a little bit of pestering, he agreed!</p>\n<p><img src=\"/image/WebsiteSetupExperience1.png\" alt=\"alt text\"></p>\n<p>He handled all the initial folder setup for me, so all I had to do was tweak some data and push it to GitHub.<br>After about two or three days, my blog is finally live! Which is exactly what you’re looking at right now!<br>I’m really grateful to everyone who helped me out these past few days, even though there was a bit of a hiccup along the way…</p>\n<p>The Hiccup<br>The normal workflow is to run <code>hexo clean</code>, <code>hexo g</code>, <code>hexo s</code> and so on, but while I was running tests, I accidentally broke the whole thing.<br>I thought about pulling the working version back from GitHub to revert the changes, but then I accidentally ran <code>hexo d</code> !!!!!!<br>Then, while trying to find the previous version in the backend, I accidentally <strong>deleted</strong> it…<br>I was honestly on the verge of a meltdown. In the end, guess how I saved it?<br><br><br><br><code>CTRL+Z</code><br><br><br><br>Well, at least I got it back.<br>And that’s pretty much the story!</p>\n<p><small>Translated By Gemini.</small></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"架設網站心得我過去一直以為Blog是甚麼老人才會用的撥接式網路那個年代的產物，結果我後來發現這東西其實蠻流行的。之前也有嘗試問AI去做但每次都不知道為甚麼都會報...","permalink":"/post/Website Setup Experience","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Hello World","slug":"Hello-World","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Hello-World.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"心得","slug":"心得","count":3,"path":"api/tags/心得.json"},{"name":"閒聊","slug":"閒聊","count":4,"path":"api/tags/閒聊.json"},{"name":"繁體中文","slug":"繁體中文","count":4,"path":"api/tags/繁體中文.json"},{"name":"EN","slug":"EN","count":1,"path":"api/tags/EN.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9E%B6%E8%A8%AD%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">架設網站心得